<Layout title="Welcome to Astro.">
	
	<main id="case-study">
		<Nav />
		<div style="position:relative; ">
        <section class="case-study--header">
            <div style="width: 800px; margin: 0 auto 3rem; display: grid; gap: 32px; text-align: center;">
                <h1 style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">Metric Explorer</h1>
                <p>A powerful tool designed for advanced analysis, offering seamless AI integration to simplify complex tasks and enhance overall ease of use. It streamlines workflows, allowing users to focus on insights rather than manual processes.</p>
            </div>
			<div class="case-study--full-container" style="margin-bottom: 5rem;" transition:name="ds">
                <figure>
                    <img src="src/assets/work-design-system--cover.png" style="width: 1200px; margin: 0rem auto 1rem; border-radius: 2rem; overflow: hidden;">
                </figure>
            </div>
           
        </section>
        <section class="case-study--body" style="">
            <div class="case-study--background">
                <h2>Project Info</h2>
                <div class="case-study--background-info-container">
                    <div class="case-study--background-info">
                        <div>
                            <h3 style="font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 16px; color: #999">Name</h3>
                            <p>Metric Explorer</p>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 style="font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 16px; color: #999">Role</h3>
                            <p>Project lead</p>
                            <p>Individual contributor</p>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 style="font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 16px; color: #999">Year</h3>
                            <p>2024</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="case-study--background">
                <h2>Background</h2>
                <div class="case-study--background-info-container">
                    <div>
                        <p>PowerMetrics lacked options for deeper, more advanced analysis of metrics and data. However, introducing this feature shouldn't alienate less experienced users. By leveraging AI tools, we can create a user-friendly solution that allows anyone to ask questions about their data and receive accurate, actionable insights.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="case-study--background">
                <h2>Issues</h2>
                <div class="case-study--background-info-container">
                    <div>
                        <p>With our transition to focus more on advanced users and integrators, PowerMetrics as a tool was still primarily used by the knowledge workers (the business user) whose data literacy level varies between different companies and different levels. It was important to allow the integrators the power to bring all sorts of data into PowerMetrics and make it a hub. But also for the knowledge worker (the business user) of all expertise levels to be able to get the insights they need and dive deep without any limitations.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="case-study--full-container" style="margin-bottom: 5rem;">
                <figure>
                    <img src="src/assets/work-explorer--metric-overview.png" style="width: 1200px; margin: 0rem auto 1rem; border-radius: 2rem; overflow: hidden;">
                    <figcaption>The Metric Homepage, provides a broad overview of the metric divded by different segments</figcaption>
                </figure>
            </div>
            <div class="case-study--background">
                <h2>Proposed solution</h2>
                <div class="case-study--background-info-container">
                    <div>
                        <p>An exploration space the accommodates everyone's level of expertise:</p>
                        <ul style="margin-top: 1rem;">
                            <li>Big open exploration space</li>
                            <li>Powerful Sidebar</li>
                            <li>Generative AI</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
			<div class="case-study--full-container" style="margin-bottom: 5rem;">
                <figure>
						<img src="src/assets/work-explorer--cover.png" style="width: 1200px; margin: 0rem auto 1rem; border-radius: 2rem; overflow: hidden;">
                    <figcaption>The Metric Homepage, provides a broad overview of the metric divded by different segments</figcaption>
                </figure>
            </div>
            <div class="case-study--full-container" style="margin-bottom: 5rem;">
                <figure>
                    <img src="src/assets/work-explorer--wireframe.png" style="width: 1200px; margin: 0rem auto 1rem; border-radius: 2rem; overflow: hidden;">
                    <figcaption>The Metric Homepage, provides a broad overview of the metric divded by different segments</figcaption>
                </figure>
            </div>
            <div class="case-study--text-container">
                <div>
                    <h3 style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">Big open exploration space</h3>
                    <p>Big open exploration space: A focus on the visualization that gives the user the breathing room to full capture every detail they need.
                    </p>
                    <p>Key Requirements:</p>
                     <ul style="margin-top: 1rem;">
                        <li>Generative </li>
                        <li>Generative </li>
                        <li>Generative </li>
                        <li>Generative </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="case-study--full-container" style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
                <figure>
                    <img src="src/assets/work-explorer--exploration-space-1.png" style="width: 1200px; margin: 0rem auto 1rem; border-radius: 2rem; overflow: hidden;">
                    <figcaption>The Metric Homepage, provides a broad overview of the metric divded by different segments</figcaption>
                </figure>
            </div>
            <div class="case-study--full-container" style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
