                </figure>
            </div>
            <div class="case-study--text-container">
                <div>
                    <h3 style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">Powerful sidebar</h3>
                    <p>Big open exploration space: A focus on the visualization that gives the user the breathing room to full capture every detail they need.
                    </p>
                    <p>Key Requirements:</p>
                    <ul style="margin-top: 1rem;">
                        <li>Generative </li>
                        <li>Generative </li>
                        <li>Generative </li>
                        <li>Generative </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="case-study--full-container" style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
                <figure>
                    <img src="src/assets/work-explorer--sidebar.png" style="width: 1200px; margin: 0rem auto 1rem; border-radius: 2rem; overflow: hidden;">
                    <figcaption>The Metric Homepage, provides a broad overview of the metric divded by different segments</figcaption>
                </figure>
            </div>
