                    <img src="src/assets/work-explorer--gen-ai.png" style="width: 1200px; margin: 0rem auto 1rem; border-radius: 2rem; overflow: hidden;">
                    <figcaption>The Metric Homepage, provides a broad overview of the metric divded by different segments</figcaption>
                </figure>
            </div>
			<div class="case-study--text-container">
                <div>
                    <h3 style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">History checkpoints</h3>
                    <p>The AI keeps context of previous requests, and that could have an impact on how it answers after. We also wanted to give the user checkpoints to get back to if they want.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="case-study--full-container" style="margin-bottom: 3rem;display: grid;grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;gap: 16px;">
                <figure>
                    <img src="src/assets/work-explorer--history1.png" style="width: 1200px; margin: 0rem auto 1rem; border-radius: 2rem; overflow: hidden;">
                    <figcaption>The Metric Homepage, provides a broad overview of the metric divded by different segments</figcaption>
                </figure>
				<figure>
